## Executive Summary

This report summarizes the results of the **{{ campaign_name }}** security scanning campaign.

### Key Metrics

| Metric | Count | Rate |
|--------|-------|------|
| Packages Scanned | {{ total_scanned }} | 100% |
| Packages Flagged | {{ total_flagged }} | {{ flag_rate }} |
| Packages Malicious | {{ total_malicious }} | {{ malicious_rate }} |

{% if total_malicious > 0 %}
